      h2 Internals
      p The styleshhet is written in <a href="http://sass-lang.com/">Sass</a> and compiled to CSS. The main file is <code>gutenweb.sass</code>, which use the helper file <code>_helper.sass</code>, where there are some usefull functions and mixins.
      p <a href="http://meyerweb.com/eric/tools/css/reset/">Eric Meyer reset stylesheet</a> is used to avoid problems with default rendering engines styles.
